  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-72ccea70-7b30-4a7a-aada-cd08a1d916eb\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-7f66454c-0d94-4783-b317-1dda710068e9\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-421684aa-667e-4485-a1a5-bab665c0806d\"><b>안녕하세요. 남성역 1번 출구에 위치하고 있는</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"line-height:1.8;\" id=\"SE-b49b0abb-0102-48d3-a964-6e7f6cd16ac3\"><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#fff593;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-d22ca19f-ee85-45df-8331-21c216e85c57\"><b>이수한의원</b></span><span style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-9797e969-cd27-4e71-a381-e5b6d7279215\"><b> 입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-72ccea70-7b30-4a7a-aada-cd08a1d916eb\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d2dfd75b-8308-4609-97b4-14a0f9eaf64a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"7\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_7.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a7a42058-bf96-4a40-93fd-920f3f005ce0\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-71d49c7c-70e6-4b19-a314-bfa1fe8c294d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4eaa96aa-11ca-48e5-8d01-6142561d33ad\">요즘은 많은 분들이 한의원에 내원해 침 치료를 받습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-90afe37a-693f-49fb-bfd6-e9061cd34ea9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a1f576e9-72ea-4a72-9827-424994632245\">&#x27;침술(鍼術)&#x27;은 우리 몸의 경혈(經穴)에 침을 놓아 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d494a4c1-d18e-4b16-8459-55b89ab2b5f0\"><b>기혈의 흐름을 조절하고, </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-61e168c5-0725-42bf-a367-200f893ae816\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b0a2e36b-eee4-45c0-9217-798559971021\"><b>통증을 완화하며, 전반적인 건강을 회복</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cf03ae05-4b34-4e45-a3f3-1ec912d85d35\">시키는 대표적인 한방 치료법입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-a7a42058-bf96-4a40-93fd-920f3f005ce0\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-1772d1e7-88aa-4ee1-ba96-bf6fb9d500cc\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-92931e5a-3ff8-47f5-af5f-e96905a1fefc\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-92931e5a-3ff8-47f5-af5f-e96905a1fefc\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ea28fe793a5a9f89.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1500\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1500\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ea28fe793a5a9f89.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ea28fe793a5a9f89.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-92931e5a-3ff8-47f5-af5f-e96905a1fefc\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-f5fc5c90-b281-459d-84f4-aeed8d253c33\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ef84f2b7-6ba9-40ae-968a-f4a0ab736b4d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6b6f3138-8684-4ee4-88ae-dff294cd28bb\"><b>침술이란?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-25ce8df3-0170-4ff7-8465-8f09d61f70c3\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0e5b6ede-f9a3-45ac-aa82-da95da5cd233\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6359d280-ee40-4157-b085-343fbe218fd7\">침술은 오랜 역사와 전통을 지닌 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-81ef56ab-c8d6-4033-815e-6a37bd7089de\"><b>한의학의 핵심 치료법</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1a238892-76c3-490a-a93c-757058efa871\"> 중 하나입니다. 경혈에 침을 자극하면 신경계, 혈액순환, 면역계 등에 영향을 주어 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-949e5778-800a-49ac-8fbc-4a9b98dfc359\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-adade71b-c4bd-4c68-89e1-7dd0aed77fad\"><b>자연치유력을 끌어올리는 역할</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-aefea554-5932-4309-bdbf-bfa267f29906\">을 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-25ce8df3-0170-4ff7-8465-8f09d61f70c3\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-57e29687-6486-42ea-8a6b-3a408790435e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-57e29687-6486-42ea-8a6b-3a408790435e\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/84d084ea5d789751.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1024\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1024\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/84d084ea5d789751.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/84d084ea5d789751.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-57e29687-6486-42ea-8a6b-3a408790435e\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-55a2fb8a-9c85-465c-a78b-af0486875054\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-4438d223-b0e2-4a78-af9a-2bb908dacd73\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b37afba6-e525-4d9e-83e0-59743c94f4be\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-78f938ff-7e98-4a1f-b96f-10de44763365\"><b>어떤 증상에 어떤 효과가?</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d173b2b5-729f-4c67-9b16-3b85ffd22dee\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-386a19d2-93f4-49cc-a6f8-1d3945d8b13a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5d8aff0b-8db9-4a90-9ab3-476048510268\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-082b73a7-08d2-4034-81ee-59f15facb439\"><b>근육통, 관절통 등 다양한 통증 질환</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-037813e8-8779-4924-98c7-f8741f17298c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b62b7b3d-8f8a-415b-95d8-74e978a54683\"><b>소화불량, 두통, 생리통 등 기능성 질환</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e969a792-1bfd-4a6a-8f6f-18fe53de53db\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f6924de8-d062-4609-8d0b-9e2689795d85\"><b>스트레스, 불면, 만성피로 같은 심신 문제</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-42423d09-0721-47af-87fc-aa7b042f32e5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a172c42f-9267-4687-8a47-208a3cfc5ac8\"><b>면역력 증진 및 체질 개선</b></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fa4160f1-168c-4ee2-b8ee-1164cd3c0dcf\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-05956a4a-4e87-4ecc-a290-312864450ddb\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dd630f12-35ac-4e65-a643-6ed600e37e23\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-83bc6c8c-2e2f-49cc-8d6e-c108bf0b6151\">특히 현대인의 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-14debfdd-3b56-4dd6-b3be-d76a680c95e3\"><b>잘못된 자세나 스트레스로 인한 통증</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a50d8538-4a03-460f-ac59-983e4b62a5b5\">에는 침술이 즉각적인 완화 효과를 주는 경우도 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-386a19d2-93f4-49cc-a6f8-1d3945d8b13a\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-decfec21-42ad-44e4-a856-7fe9c697b4e1\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-2e4a1b95-f006-4f08-b7e9-d185a8ed8ffd\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8e63f498-cf9a-4436-a965-a946067961b2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8da4b64b-974c-4fbe-ba4d-db2f6dae6b6d\"><b>주의사항</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n         